user_description: Research news, events and health tips from UVA Health.
text:
@PEHJackson explains that all vaccines have a very low myocarditis risk, but this risk is higher in younger males. The Johnson & Johnson vaccine doesn't have any association with this side effect and may be the better option for some. #CovidVaccine
